### When shadcn Doesn't Have It

1. **Check shadcn blocks**: https://ui.shadcn.com/blocks (pre-built complex UI)
2. **Use Radix primitives**: https://radix-ui.com/primitives (accessible base components)
3. **Build with Tailwind**: Use tokens from `@worksite/ui/tokens` and CSS variables

### Code Standards

```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT - Always use cn() for class merging
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils';

<Button className={cn('custom-class', isActive && 'active-class')}>
  Click me
</Button>

// ✅ CORRECT - Use lucide-react for icons
